<HEADLINE> Stone Agrees To Give NBK Deposition </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	AMITE, La. (AP) -- Oliver Stone apparently has agreed to give a  
deposition in a lawsuit accusing his movie, ``Natural Born 
Killers,'' of triggering a violent attack. 
</P>
<P>
	Stone and his lawyers plan to be in Louisiana later this year to  
testify in the case, according to the lawyer for the plaintiffs, 
Joe Simpson. 
</P>
<P>
	Simpson is suing Stone and Time Warner, the movie's distributor,  
on behalf of the family of Patsy Byers. The convenience store clerk 
